Implementation Roadmap:

```python
def deploy_maya_health_system(hospital_network):
    deployment_phases = {
        'phase_1': 'Community Health Foundation - Preventive Care',
        'phase_2': 'Diagnostic Platform - Primary Care Integration',
        'phase_3': 'Temple Specialists - Treatment Coordination',
        'phase_4': 'Health Observatory - Research & Innovation',
        'phase_5': 'Sacred Integration - Whole Person Care'
    }
    
    health_system = MayaDigitalHealthSystem(hospital_network)
    return health_system.comprehensive_patient_care("population_health")
```

